{"tid":2188762,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★【新貴出爐】信達康基等獲納入港股通 下周一生效","createTime":"2020-09-04T12:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T12:24:19.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0c526a018fa1ab57643450a70d723076d0ce2937","tid":2188762,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:23:59.000Z","msg":"港股通微信公眾號公佈，因應恒生綜合大型股指數、中型股指數、小型股指數實施成份股定期調整，港股通股票名單將自9月7日起調整。<br />\n<br />\n滬港通下的港股通股票名單，共有10隻調入、11隻調出。深港通下的港股通股票名單，共有24隻調入、15隻調出。當中，信達生物、百濟神州（6160），及康基醫療（9997），及鷹君（041）等同時獲納入滬港通及深港通名單。<br />\n<br />\n滬港通新貴金地商置（535）、微創醫療（853）、香港寬頻（1310）、新東方在綫（1797）、信達生物（1801）、中海物業（2669）等。<br />\n<br />\n深港通新貴則有九毛九（9922）、移卡（9928）、日清（1475）、海吉亞醫療（6078）等。<br />\n<br />\n和記電訊（215）、華寶國際（336）、大新金融（440）、浙江滬杭甬（576）、豐盛（607）、首控（1269）、美圖（1357）、莎莎（178）等被剔出港股通。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200904/DWZU2ZB6DNBZPD24VPEZV4W2WQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200904%2FDWZU2ZB6DNBZPD24VPEZV4W2WQ%2F&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cRYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=427f4379\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200904%2FDWZU2ZB6DNBZPD24VPEZV4W2WQ%2F&h=0558f2ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200904/DWZU2ZB6DNBZPD24VPEZV4W2WQ/</a>"},{"pid":"c9cade4b9add696aaec24e49e3cf999b44840b68","tid":2188762,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}